data.description: This spacious, move-in ready tri-level property is ready for you to make it home. Boasting a brand new roof with gutters, fresh interior and exterior paint, updated bathroom tile, new kitchen backsplash, along with brand new carpet and lvp flooring throughout—- there’s so much to fall in love with. Add in the benefit of great natural lighting, multiple living spaces, a formal dining space and a large laundry/storage room. Plus the big back yard, with two sizable sheds and covered concrete patio provides plenty of options for the family and pets to enjoy. Be sure to check out this home today!
